queries.sql: SELECT *, count(mo_moviecate.movie_id) as movie_nb FROM mo_category inner JOIN mo_moviecate ON mo_category.category_id = mo_moviecate.category_id WHERE `mo_category`.branch_id = 1 GROUP BY mo_category.category_id

SELECT mo_movie.*, mo_slide.slide_img FROM mo_movie INNER JOIN mo_slide ON mo_slide.movie_id = mo_movie.movie_id WHERE `mo_movie`.branch_id = '1' AND `mo_movie`.movie_active = '1' ORDER BY `mo_slide`.slide_id ASC
